description:
Secrets agents who control feudal lords in the Nayutaya country.
The group consists of:
Imonoyama Nokoru (妹之山残) who is originally from Clamp Gakuen Tanteidan series and appeard also in X movie.
Takamura Suou (鷹村蘇芳) who is originally from Clamp Gakuen Tanteidan series and appeard also in X movie.
Ijuuin Akira (伊集院玲) who is originally from 20 Mensou ni Onegai (20面相におねがい!!) manga and appeared also in Clamp Gakuen Tanteidan series and in X movie.
name: Mitteishuu
